creator: John Clare
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 7 recordings of Schoolboys in Winter by John Clare. This was the Weekly Poetry project for January 4th, 2015. Read in English by A.J. Tippin; Algy Pug; Bruce Kachuk; David Lawrence; Esther ben Simonides; Lee Ann Howlett & Maria Kasper This poem depicts the outdoor activities of a group of boys on their way to school. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org./>
